other applicable provisions of law.
Proposed law is intended to ensure compliance with applicable federal and state laws and
regulations governing criminal history record information, including particular federal
regulations and of the Federal Bureau of Investigations (FBI).
Proposed law does not authorize the redissemination of criminal history record information
obtained from the FBI.
